<p class="ql-align-justify">“有一次晚上我老板，凌晨三点给我发消息，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">我没有回，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他觉得，完了，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">李雪琴‘死’了。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/1b68261b900f468ab82f89a5fcf723fc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">下一秒，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">领笑人大张伟爆灯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200901/a8df8c095a374e68aec178548cbf9d6a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">表演结束后，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">李诞忍不住问大张伟，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">你拍灯的点，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">实在太古怪了，</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
